Create SKILL.md file for content review agent content-review-agent.py. The python agent should load anthropic key from .env file. The python code should ask user for a multi-line text input that needs to be analyzed and will first check for any PII (personal identifiable info) in the input data using Clause API. PII includes names, email, phone number, address, SSN, credit card info, health information, etc. If there is PII the program immediately exits. If there is no PII data, the program asks the user what to do with the text. Then the python code should use claude API to answer the user questions. All output should be in JSON and should contain a key that represents if Claude is confident in its answer. Keep the answers short and the tone friendly. If the confidence level is low, then Claude and the python code should ask the user clarifying questions - max 3 times. After that the user is asked if they are satisfied with the answer. If yes, the program exits. If no, the user is asked to enter clarifying questions - max 3 times.

